title: Walk In Your Father's Shoes | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Walk In Your Father's Shoes | Victoria Osteen
description:
Whatever you're facing today, know that God has all the strength you need. When you grab hold of His strength, He will take you to places you've never dreamed.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
